<section id="HE92EB89C05A147DAA621001B043B5246" section-type="section-one"><enum>1.</enum><header>Short title</header><text display-inline="no-display-inline">This Act may be cited as the <quote><short-title>The Bureau of Corrections Renaming Act of 2015</short-title></quote>.</text></section> <section id="HC0C024C12FB541BFAF1D4D2D0F0BF34D" section-type="subsequent-section"><enum>2.</enum><header>Renaming of Bureau of Prisons</header> <subsection id="HB49AC6E3230546AA8F177BC034B237A4"><enum>(a)</enum><header>In general</header><text>The Bureau of Prisons in the Department of Justice is renamed the <term>Bureau of Corrections</term>.</text></subsection> 
