<paragraph display-inline="no-display-inline" id="H1708326A033D4ACBA355CFC4F2D28581"><enum>(42)</enum><text>Section 231 of <external-xref legal-doc="public-law" parsable-cite="pl/110/199">Public Law 110–199</external-xref>.</text></paragraph></subsection> <subsection id="H385C8CF4335D4C359CF495F4742A6844"><enum>(c)</enum><header>Treatment of other references to Bureau of Prisons</header><text>Each reference to the Bureau of Prisons in the laws and regulations of the United States, other than those amended in subsection (b), shall be deemed a reference to the Bureau of Corrections.</text></subsection></section> 
